  <h2>
    <span class="">作者简介</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>



      <div class="indent ">
          
            <div class="">
            <style type="text/css" media="screen">
.intro p{text-indent:2em;word-break:normal;}
</style>
<div class="intro">
    <p>查尔斯•金，美国乔治敦大学国际事务与政府学教授。他经常作为全球问题评论员出现在媒体上，主要著作有Odessa：Genius and Death in a City of Dreams; Extreme Politics: Essays on Nationalism, Violence, and Eastern Europe; The Black Sea: A History; 等等。现居华盛顿。</p></div>

